"Processes are what help people scale up in their businesses. Look at your processes and standardize them." - @gkbalogs of @sofreshng on the #FidelitySMEForum

"Delivery will continue to be on the rise. So you have to look at how you can deliver your products and services to people, especially at this time." - @gkbalogs of @sofreshng on the #FidelitySMEForum
"In starting up a food business, you need to identify what exactly you are selling and why you should be the preferred choice." - @gkbalogs of @sofreshng on the #FidelitySMEForum
"Take a look at all your processes to see where the hazards are and then find ways to mitigate those hazards." - @gkbalogs of @sofreshng on the #FidelitySMEForum
"Stay close to your customers by engaging them on social media. Consider doing some discounts and freebies to stimulate sales." - @gkbalogs of @sofreshng on the #FidelitySMEForum
"What’s most important for any food business at this time is to be able to operate safely." - @gkbalogs of @sofreshng on the #FidelitySMEForum
"As a business person, it’s important that you take data seriously." - @gkbalogs on the #FidelitySMEForum
